metadata.name: The sensuality of a wild rose
metadata.description:
Not all roses have thorns, but be careful in your words and actions, you may get hurt. I drew this girl who looks like me in my inner feelings. She is beautiful and gentle, emotionally filled, you want to touch her, but you need to be careful, do not scare her, do not offend her, otherwise she will prick you with her thorns. â €
